<tbody>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Item search fields</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate the search fields to show in the <strong>Rebooking</strong> menu.<br>
